      "value": "<p>The new user interface for RenderMan for Maya is composed of a number of sections.</p><ul class=\"childpages-macro conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"ebdb5254-eca4-4683-8e35-744104994b91\" data-macro-id=\"fbba0c69-6733-49bf-ad41-bacab0c4302b\" data-macro-name=\"children\"><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544538944/RenderMan+Shelf\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538944\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Shelf</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539259/RenderMan+Menu\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539259\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Menu</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539308/RenderMan+Preferences\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539308\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Preferences</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539520/Supported+Maya+Nodes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539520\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Supported Maya Nodes</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539547/String+tokens+in+RfM\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539547\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">String tokens in RfM</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539564/Preset+Browser+in+Maya\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539564\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Preset Browser in Maya</a></li></ul><p><br/></p><p>Note that some nodes may have available presets you can use by selecting the triple bar &quot;sandwich&quot; next to parameters</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"456\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538919/presetsMayaUI.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431536130&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=302\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544538919/presetsMayaUI.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431536130&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"302\" data-width=\"446\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544538931\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"presetsMayaUI.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544538919\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"39bb51fe-05a0-4c65-b57f-3b901d6a25e0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538919/presetsMayaUI.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431536130&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=302 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544538919/presetsMayaUI.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431536130&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=302 1x\"></span><p><br/></p>"
